bib_statements.li: Association d'études et d'informations politiques internationales.
Gift of the DeWitt Wallace Endowment Fund, named in honor of the founder of Reader's Digest

bn.li: Separately paged supplements accompany some numbers.

Issued by Association d'études et d'informations politiques internationales, 1956-May/June 1983; jointly by Association d'études politiques internationales and Institut d'histoire sociale, <1984>-Mar. 1993.
Spanish ed., which began publication in 1962, has title: Este & oeste.
Has separately cataloged supplement: Supplément de Est & ouest; [brochure].
